      "time": "~20s",
      "narrative": "- Start where the business feels the pressure.\n- More CMO activity means more invoices, more terms to check, and more room for payment mistakes.\n- Waypoint is how Pharma Company reviews invoices against the full operating record before money goes out the door.",
      "demo_actions": "Open the Waypoint invoices tab. Show a list of invoices with visible statuses: matched, variance, and disputed. Pause on the totals and counts at the top.",
