      },
      "time": "~25s",
      "narrative": "- This is about dollars, not just flags.\n- Show what is ready to pay.\n- Show what needs review.\n- Show where recovery opportunity or compliance risk is starting to build.",
      "demo_actions": "Point to dollar amounts tied to matched, variance, and disputed invoices. Sort or filter to surface the highest-value exceptions.",
      "screenshot": ".cutready/screenshots/20260617_111253_CleanShot 2026-06-17 at 11.11.27@2x.png"
