        "narrative": false,
        "demo_actions": false,
        "screenshot": false,
        "visual": false,
        "design_plan": false
      },
      "time": "~40s",
      "narrative": "- Now compare that with an invoice that does not line up.\n- Waypoint shows the gap clearly.\n- It ties the issue back to the source record.\n- The team can act on facts instead of email threads and manual checks.",
      "demo_actions": "Open a variance or disputed invoice. Highlight the specific mismatch, such as rate, quantity, milestone, timing, or release status. Show linked evidence and the system's decision rationale.",
      "screenshot": ".cutready/screenshots/20260617_111347_CleanShot 2026-06-17 at 11.13.26@2x.png"
    },
    {
