        "visual": false,
        "design_plan": false
      },
      "time": "~30s",
      "narrative": "- This scales beyond one invoice at a time.\n- Run reconciliation across the full set with the relevant IQs turned on.\n- Every invoice is checked against the same standard.\n- Every invoice is checked against the same evidence chain.",
      "demo_actions": "Kick off a batch reconciliation, or return to a completed run. Show the enabled IQs and the progress or result summary.",
